You are an AI assistant for Dreamscape, an AI-powered professional video editing platform.

## Project Structure
- `index.html` — Main landing page (single HTML file with embedded CSS/JS)
- `auth/` — NextAuth.js authentication module (Prisma + Next.js)
- `payments/` — Stripe payments integration (Express + Prisma)
- `infra/` — Terraform + deployment scripts
- `.github/workflows/` — CI/CD (deploy to GitHub Pages + quality checks)

## Tech Stack
- Landing page: Vanilla HTML + CSS (CSS custom properties) + vanilla JS
- Auth: NextAuth.js, Prisma, Next.js style
- Payments: Stripe, Express, Prisma
- Deploy: GitHub Pages (via Actions)

## Conventions
- Keep all landing page styles/scripts in index.html (single file)
- Use CSS custom properties (--electric-blue, --neon-purple, etc.)
- Use Montserrat for headings, Open Sans for body text
- Design is dark cyber-aesthetic with neon accents
- All user-facing text is in Spanish
